## Mock Response: `streamDoc` (documentationChain)

**Trigger keyword in prompt:** `"srs"` | `"sdd"` | `"brief"`
**Behaviour:** The mock calls `onToken()` once per sentence fragment (simulating streaming), then calls `onComplete()`.

**Mock SRS token sequence (truncated — full output simulated):**
```
"# Software Requirements Specification\n"
"## TaskFlow Pro\n\n"
"### 1. Introduction\n"
"TaskFlow Pro is a collaborative task management application..."
"[... more tokens ...]"
```

**Mock SDD token sequence:**
```
"# Software Design Document\n"
"## System Architecture\n\n"
"The system follows a RESTful client-server architecture..."
```

**Mock Brief token sequence:**
```
"## App Brief: TaskFlow Pro\n\n"
"**What it does:** Helps small teams manage tasks with a Kanban board...\n"
```

